  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n*Summary*: Text of message is not formatted accordingly on home screen when message in chat (1-1  / public) sent wrapped up with asterisks (`*`) or tildes (`~`)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nText of message formatted on home screen in **bold**/_italic_ font when message in chat sent wrapped up with asterisks (`*`) or tildes (`~`)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nText of message is not formatted on home screen in **bold**/_italic_ font when message in chat sent wrapped up with asterisks (`*`) or tildes (`~`)\r\n![desk_bold](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/43130213-dc00e030-8f3e-11e8-83f4-2bf064a84329.png)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Join any public chat\r\n- Send message wrapped up with asterisks and tildes (e.g. `*Bold*, ~Italic~ fonts`)\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: status desktop 22/07/18\r\n[comment]: # (Android or iOS.)\r\n* Operating System: Mac OSx\r\n",
